creator: uShip Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Take the world's largest and most trusted transportation marketplace on-the-go with the official Android app. Everything uShip offers, available in a streamlined, user friendly interface all in the palm your hand!

Service Providers:

The uShip for Android app powers your business when you’re on the road. It makes finding, bidding on, and booking shipments faster and more effective! You will never miss the opportunity to book a shipment and will maximize your time on the road!
• View and manage your active, booked and completed shipments.
• Make getting paid easier with uShip payments
• Use saved searches to get access to your most effective routes with a simple tap.

Shippers:

Managing your listing and communication with your service provider has never been easier using the uShip for Android app.
• Ask questions and get answers fast!
• Pay your service provider quickly and securely with uShip payments.
• View and manage your active, booked and completed listings in one simple mobile solution.

Making our app as easy as possible is our #1 priority. We want to hear how we can make it even better. Send us your comments and suggestions at androidapp@uship.com.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Electronic Bill of Lading (eBOL): Paperlessly document shipment pickup and delivery. Add photos, notes and signatures all from the uShip app to create a PDF record of your shipment.

* Carriers can share eBOL access with their drivers without a uShip account
* PDF automatically available to carrier and shipper
* Supports contactless delivery to ensure efficiency and safety
